job.title: IIPS Assistant Professors Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for Various Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:09

Name of the post:

  • Assistant Professor & Associate Professor

Description:

International Institute for Population Sciences issued a total of 09 vacancies for the posts of Assistant Professor & Associate Professor. The online application for these posts under IIPS shall start from 05.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 31.05.2021 For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com.The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for IIPS Assistant Professors Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 05.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 31.05.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the Degree in M. Phil, Ph.D. To apply for the post of Assistant Professor & Associate Professor

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is:21 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is:37 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post, Assistant Professor & Associate Professor is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

How to apply for IIPS Assistant Professors Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of IIPS
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Assistant Professor & Associate Professor
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
